column4:
Good Morning,

I am Josh Les, Purchasing Specialist at HIDRAVLIKA S.r.l., I hope this message finds you well.

Following up on the email sent to you by our Sales Director, Mr. Gibertini which we have not received any reply from you, I would like to kindly request your commercial offer for the listed items in our attached RFQ.

Also, we request you to fill also the attached suppliers data form and send me the filled and signed form for our confirmation at your earliest possible.


I remain at your disposal for any further information and thank you in advance for your cooperation.

Best regards,

***Josh Les***
*Purchasing Specialist*

**HIDRAVLIKA S.r.l.**
Via Giovanni Agnelli, 3
10070 FIANO (TO)
ITALY
Tel. +39/011/9269240 - Fax +39/011/9269833
P.IVA 05141240019
Iscritto Registro delle Imprese di Torino
Registrazione numero 05141240019

If you have wrongly received this message, please notify us immediately so we can make sure it gets to the right person**. Thank you.*

Thanks and best regards
